{"tid":1070192,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺住公屋嘅人皮膚特別差？","createTime":"2019-03-20T12:55:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T16:18:13.000Z","uid":241093,"like":23,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9844dd4c873470ab0e1cdd52ae7514533425c240","tid":1070192,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T12:55:37.000Z","msg":"班油頭暗瘡毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日對住公屋廢老 廢中 腥移民<br />\n索得廢氣多 物以類聚 想皮膚好都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人哋住私樓<br />\n無論大堂定屋企都起碼有部空氣清新機<br />\n間唔中有專人幫你開門 㩒𨋢<br />\n得閒有錢買下護膚品 做下facial <br />\n細菌都冇咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公屋仔 臭罌岀臭草<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一世都有寒酸味 繼續生暗瘡濕疹喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5c9cc35241fd530d8cdfaffabe94b7fbc80817","tid":1070192,"uid":181997,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T12:56:09.000Z","msg":"你個名"},{"pid":"2e8d755f9ebfbabee57b040379f344e0fa43ff87","tid":1070192,"uid":123456,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:00:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你收聲<br />\n私樓狗又唔抵得我地租平</span></span>"},{"pid":"9f1dd7a084cb4e73008ac9e3c2e7a791824f20d9","tid":1070192,"uid":172411,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好咁話自己啦"},{"pid":"89f968f309d14e2fcdf515584e02556c7336aece","tid":1070192,"uid":3302,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T13:01:01.000Z","msg":"agger<br />\n公屋仔特別低賤<br />\n拎盡社會資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcbbf7a5f25f09d2fb9df613993ce461e65c0ac","tid":1070192,"uid":40272